OL,5, A man has been found guilty of causing 
OL,6, intentional harassment, alarm or       
OL,7, distress after scaring female motorists
OL,8, while dressed in a gimp suit.          
OL,10,FJoshua Hunt, 32, of Claverham, was seen
OL,11,Fby one woman writhing around on the    
OL,12,Fground, while another said she was left
OL,13,Fshaking and crying after an encounter. 
OL,15,FBristol Magistrates' Court heard the   
OL,16,Fincidents took place on 7 and 9 May in 
OL,17,FBleadon, Somerset.                     
OL,19,FHunt, a self-employed gardener, had    
OL,20,Fdenied the allegations.                
